{"tid":1409633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」唔好阻住我番工","createTime":"2019-08-04T23:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:29:23.000Z","uid":276245,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa6d083de96bf9146ffa448dbddd0edfe32528a","tid":1409633,"uid":276245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:08:57.000Z","msg":"// 反對激進人士堵路 汀九屬高危<br />\n<br />\n各位支持特區政府的讀者們，明天反對派和激進示威者，一定會盡一切方法，阻礙熱愛工作的香港人上班。而我城最脆弱的幹道之一，就是汀九橋！<br />\n<br />\n汀九橋(A)連接屯門公路和三號幹線！如果汀九橋被阻，所有車輛🚗就被迫駛往屯門公路往荃灣方向(B)和青山公路往荃灣方向(C)!到時，反對派的圖謀就有機會得逞！幸好，香港的執法者效率很高，一定可以避免上述事情發生！<br />\n<br />\n所以，我們守法、愛港的讀者們，和所有的香港市民，一定不可以參加、組織和支持任何堵塞道路的行為！香港亂不起，我們要穩定！// <br />\n<br />\n我要番工啊😡希望大家俾條生路我行下<br />\n<br />\n轉載自：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/227321757363217/posts/2290874257674613?s=1270157170&amp;substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F227321757363217%2Fposts%2F2290874257674613%3Fs%3D1270157170%26substory_index%3D0%26sfns%3Dmo&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QobeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=ed1a27ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/227321757363217/posts/2290874257674613?s=1270157170&amp;substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"03767b0f56b4246bc30e85f0166c24983f9879cd","tid":1409633,"uid":40743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c712538db1331cb1ee33c39cac507ae88c693f94","tid":1409633,"uid":5676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:29:23.000Z","msg":"熱愛工作既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你當個個人都鬼上身？"}]}